{"tid":1154770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那黑幫拍片嗆聲 惹怒柬埔寨警方跨國追緝","createTime":"2019-05-14T13:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T15:29:52.000Z","uid":32511,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7bfc7a722f3f4b4ef7fddcdb1145beb19dca3ff0","tid":1154770,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpdozglZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpdozglZ.jpg&h=bcb51673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一批號稱來自中國重慶的男子，在網上公布一則影片，嗆聲柬埔寨西哈努克省治安是他們說了算，這部短片惹怒柬埔寨警方，公開表示將展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n香港《星島日報》報導，網上流傳的影片內容是「未來三年，西港（西哈努克港）亂不亂，我們重慶人說了算！好不好？」，而發話男子囂張喊話後，身後十餘名赤裸上身的男子舉拳呼應，其中有些人是滿身紋身。<br />\n<br />\n這段影片讓柬埔寨警方十分不爽，認為破壞當地治安，從警察總署到西哈努克省警方總動員，誓言將他們緝拿到案。並且已向中國駐柬大使館提出要求，採取兩國聯合辦案模式進行，已獲得同意。<br />\n<br />\n就在事件鬧大的同時，有網友發現，在一個柬埔寨網站上，有自稱是當事人的網民留言，指那「惡搞視頻」，只是好玩，不清楚為何流傳，還是是無心觸犯法律，若是真觸法，願意接受處理，不過，這段留言未被證實是當事人留言。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EI0lb_1IbBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEI0lb_1IbBQ&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=58d2a2a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EI0lb_1IbBQ</a>"},{"pid":"b47ea8993c7245c7d3aae3cc95afd5c416fba085","tid":1154770,"uid":50101,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"成班豬肉佬做乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10619afa7ecd48cf9e28f75ec380473a19c3efc","tid":1154770,"uid":11148,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:32:34.000Z","msg":"䘈螛了，蛾的蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999b14e9f1fae51cb7a7fed42af72bd3b508e0a5","tid":1154770,"uid":43161,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:33:44.000Z","msg":"鳩叫完就淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十足十廢支那作為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22065538b0a7d0f846030163ac8500230c6873fb","tid":1154770,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:41:27.000Z","msg":"中國除咗共產黨會有其他黑社會<br />\n人唔笑狗都笑啦"},{"pid":"121b6a72acaaa0a794b03f22b3c4c4f217f69567","tid":1154770,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:42:06.000Z","msg":"呢班友人工夾埋有無兩皮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b2a0c3e5ee003dff877b67148f4df1c015a7f3","tid":1154770,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:51:30.000Z","msg":"一班得把聲既白痴仔"},{"pid":"8ceb3070e5fa9abeb922dcc8db259e5cd8c06edb","tid":1154770,"uid":118973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:05:21.000Z","msg":"忍刀大個咗"},{"pid":"b0722478237cc32a85e6ba69c0e73d78040fb572","tid":1154770,"uid":89530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQOBj1K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQOBj1K.jpg&h=ad452acc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea755ae95c285c11cf2a08749c56b76a6e890218","tid":1154770,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T15:29:52.000Z","msg":"香港好快都咁架啦，串下大陸人，黑警就同公安聯合行動捉你返大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑啦港豬，我未見個一個國家會咁唔保護自己人，仲要比人入黎捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}